Hi, I'm Chris as you can tell from my username and I will be making some KSP gameplay videos. If you have some spare time for me or have nothing else to do, please checkout my channel!

http://youtube.com/imawesomechris

I have only uploaded 1 video today, but since I love the game very much I will be uploading much more videos in upcoming time and hopefully it will be better quality for you to watch! Thanks and have a good day.
